{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"bxqmsolrgfu4fm16m5acii7","title":"reference node","desc":"","updated":1764327509431,"created":1755977777704,"custom":{},"fname":"mesh-resource.node.reference","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"documentation","selfContained":false,"name":"sflo"},"contentHash":"45d52ca2d90f170ca9c8452052812308","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"mesh-resource.node.reference","id":"bxqmsolrgfu4fm16m5acii7","vaultName":"sflo"},"value":"mesh-resource.node","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":27,"offset":42},"end":{"line":4,"column":49,"offset":64},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"mesh-resource.node"}},{"from":{"fname":"concept.mesh","id":"h6ssv16gdyf56gg235dxv85","vaultName":"sflo"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":5,"offset":1274},"end":{"line":23,"column":53,"offset":1322},"indent":[]},"value":"mesh-resource.node.reference"},{"from":{"fname":"concept.mesh","id":"h6ssv16gdyf56gg235dxv85","vaultName":"sflo"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":39,"column":69,"offset":2334},"end":{"line":39,"column":101,"offset":2366},"indent":[]},"value":"mesh-resource.node.reference"},{"from":{"fname":"concept.mesh","id":"h6ssv16gdyf56gg235dxv85","vaultName":"sflo"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":127,"column":7,"offset":9452},"end":{"line":127,"column":55,"offset":9500},"indent":[]},"value":"mesh-resource.node.reference"},{"from":{"fname":"mesh-resource.node","id":"mesh-node","vaultName":"sflo"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":3,"offset":589},"end":{"line":13,"column":35,"offset":621},"indent":[]},"value":"mesh-resource.node.reference"},{"from":{"fname":"mesh-resource.node.payload","id":"payload-node","vaultName":"sflo"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":6,"column":23,"offset":305},"end":{"line":6,"column":55,"offset":337},"indent":[]},"value":"mesh-resource.node.reference"}],"anchors":{"definition":{"type":"header","text":"Definition","value":"definition","line":8,"column":0,"depth":2},"purpose":{"type":"header","text":"Purpose","value":"purpose","line":12,"column":0,"depth":2},"typical-contents":{"type":"header","text":"Typical Contents","value":"typical-contents","line":18,"column":0,"depth":2},"core-description":{"type":"header","text":"Core Description","value":"core-description","line":20,"column":0,"depth":3},"dataset-level-description-if-the-thing-is-a-dataset":{"type":"header","text":"Dataset-level description (if the thing is a dataset)","value":"dataset-level-description-if-the-thing-is-a-dataset","line":30,"column":0,"depth":3},"context--external-perspectives":{"type":"header","text":"Context / External Perspectives","value":"context--external-perspectives","line":38,"column":0,"depth":3},"example-snapshot-distribution":{"type":"header","text":"Example Snapshot Distribution","value":"example-snapshot-distribution","line":43,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"mesh-node","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"reference-node\">reference node<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#reference-node\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"definition\">Definition<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#definition\"></a></h2>\n<p>A <strong>reference node</strong> is a <a href=\"/sflo/notes/mesh-node\">mesh node</a> that represents the (non-dataset) <strong>referent</strong> of the node — i.e., the thing in the world that the node stands for.</p>\n<h2 id=\"purpose\">Purpose<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#purpose\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>To describe what the node <em>refers to</em> (person, place, concept, dataset, etc.).</li>\n<li>To supply human/machine labels, identifiers, and minimal provenance about the referent.</li>\n<li>To differentiate between metadata about the <strong>node itself</strong> (<code>_meta</code>) and metadata about the <strong>referent</strong>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"typical-contents\">Typical Contents<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#typical-contents\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"core-description\">Core Description<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#core-description\"></a></h3>\n<p>What is the node’s referent? This is what the HTML resource page uses to say:</p>\n<p>“This is an Organization / Ontology / Rate Plan / Dataset / Whatever.”</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>rdfs:label</code> (human-readable name of the referent).</li>\n<li><code>rdf:type</code> (classifying what kind of thing the referent is).</li>\n<li>maybe  skos:prefLabel, dcterms:description, owl:sameAs, etc.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"dataset-level-description-if-the-thing-is-a-dataset\">Dataset-level description (if the thing is a dataset)<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#dataset-level-description-if-the-thing-is-a-dataset\"></a></h3>\n<ul>\n<li>Optional provenance (creator, source, temporal scope).</li>\n<li>Optional identifiers (sameAs links, external URIs).</li>\n<li>dcat:Dataset, dcat:distribution, dcterms:issued, dcterms:modified, dcterms:license, etc.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>This describes the dataset-as-thing.</p>\n<h3 id=\"context--external-perspectives\">Context / External Perspectives<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#context--external-perspectives\"></a></h3>\n<p>Links to registries, catalogs, external provenance, ie. alternate descriptions imported from elsewhere.</p>\n<h2 id=\"example-snapshot-distribution\">Example Snapshot Distribution<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#example-snapshot-distribution\"></a></h2>\n<pre class=\"language-trig\"><code class=\"language-trig\"><span class=\"token comment\"># The referent of the node (the actual person)</span>\n<span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>djradon<span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n    <span class=\"token function\"><span class=\"token prefix\">rdf<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span></span><span class=\"token local-name\">type</span></span> <span class=\"token function\"><span class=\"token prefix\">foaf<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span></span><span class=\"token local-name\">Person</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\"><span class=\"token prefix\">rdfs<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span></span><span class=\"token local-name\">label</span></span> <span class=\"token string\">\"dj radon\"</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token function\"><span class=\"token prefix\">foaf<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span></span><span class=\"token local-name\">mbox</span></span> <span class=\"token url\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&#x3C;</span>mailto:djradon@example.org<span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sflo/notes/h6ssv16gdyf56gg235dxv85\">semantic mesh</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sflo/notes/mesh-node\">mesh node</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sflo/notes/payload-node\">paylod node</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"voy7zrf0f6bs86m02uadhaf","title":"Semantic Flow Documentation","desc":"","updated":1756155165637,"created":1755709990079,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"documentation","selfContained":false,"name":"sflo"},"contentHash":"98cbbdb73a40d62308166fed9c2f594f","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"voy7zrf0f6bs86m02uadhaf","vaultName":"sflo"},"value":"now","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":1,"offset":107},"end":{"line":4,"column":8,"offset":114},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"now"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"voy7zrf0f6bs86m02uadhaf","vaultName":"sflo"},"value":"todo","position":{"start":{"line":4,"column":11,"offset":117},"end":{"line":4,"column":19,"offset":125},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,